reviewText:
A window to a parallel universe!
Animation software designed by astro physicists such as:
Jim Bardeen and mathematician Dr. F. Kenton Musgrave, using math fractal designs and not stage props!
Created using the most advanced world and terrain building software for 3D animation.
Visually stunning virtual worlds!

These parallel worlds have always existed, but its only recently we have had the machines to reveal them....
Created using the award winning animation software
Mojo World.
Visit 18 unexplored worlds in an sci-fi adventure for the eyes and ears.
